title: Young Catalans march for independence
description:
In the Spanish region of Catalonia, an independence vote has been outlawed by the governments in Madrid. 

Police forces have seized ballot boxes and arrested polling officials, but despite that more than 60% of the population are expected to cast their vote.

Sky's Diplomatic Editor Dominic Waghorn reports from Barcelona.
